text: Khanewal is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Khanewal may also refer to: *Khanewal District, district of South Punjab. *Khanewal Tehsil, tehsil of Khanewal district ==Railway stations== *Khanewal Junction railway station *Khanewal- Wazirabad Branch Line ==See also== *Khanowal, village in India * *
